{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-143","title":"同情安慰鼓励","sectionId":"chapter-07","sectionTitle":"喜怒哀乐听你说","pageStart":724,"pageEnd":727,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":14,"duplicateEntryCount":18,"pages":[{"number":724,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"143 同情安慰鼓励"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"pity [ˈpɪti]","headword":"pity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.怜悯；憾事"},{"type":"entry","text":"sympathy [ˈsɪmpəθi]","headword":"sympathy"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.同情；（思想感情上的）赞同"},{"type":"note","text":"◎express sympathy表示同情/sympathy for对…表示同情/sympathy with"},{"type":"text","text":"赞同"},{"type":"entry","text":"relief [rɪˈliːf]","headword":"relief"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.安慰"}]},{"number":725,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"heartening [ˈhɑːtnɪŋ]","headword":"heartening"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.鼓舞人心的"}]},{"number":726,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"sympathise [ˈsɪmpəθaɪz]","headword":"sympathise"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.同情；赞同"},{"type":"note","text":"◎sympathise with同情"},{"type":"entry","text":"poor thing 可怜的人","headword":"poor thing"},{"type":"entry","text":"deepest sympathy 深切的同情","headword":"deepest sympathy"},{"type":"entry","text":"heartfelt condolence 诚挚的慰问","headword":"heartfelt condolence"},{"type":"entry","text":"settle down 安定下来","headword":"settle down"},{"type":"entry","text":"take a deep breath 深呼吸","headword":"take a deep breath"},{"type":"entry","text":"nothing serious 没什么大不了的","headword":"nothing serious"}]},{"number":727,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"keep trying 继续努力","headword":"keep trying"},{"type":"entry","text":"stick it out 坚持到底","headword":"stick it out"},{"type":"entry","text":"let it go 放下吧，任由它去","headword":"let it go"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：My sister is not dealing well with the loss of her relative. （我姐"},{"type":"text","text":"姐还没有从失去亲人的痛苦中缓过来。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：That's a pity. （太遗憾了。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：My uncle died yesterday. （我叔叔昨天去世了。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：You have my sympathy. I know you were close. （我很同情你。"},{"type":"text","text":"我知道你们关系很好。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 3"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I can't believe you would do this to me. （我真不敢相信你竟这"},{"type":"text","text":"样对我。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：I feel like killing myself, if it's any consolation.（我恨不得杀了"},{"type":"text","text":"自己，如果这样能安慰你的话。）"}]}]}